{"tid":1525844,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾暴徒連野都唔識掉,大家千祈唔好學","createTime":"2019-09-01T03:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T03:56:50.000Z","uid":123615,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a49ad2008e4bb29dc0eed3100bc137b71092f60d","tid":1525844,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:14:54.000Z","msg":"睇電視睇到班暴徒就火滾,連野都唔識掉<br />\n大家就千奇唔好學佢地咁,俾人笑到面都黃<br />\n佢地拎樽底由上而下就梗係掉得唔遠啦, 係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拎樽咀由下而上</span>咁架<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有無去過運動會玩鐵餅<br />\n好似第一個小妹妹咁,側身由下而上咁擲就最遠啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=koVJdM2NtKM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkoVJdM2NtKM&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8bx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=1ed2013a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=koVJdM2NtKM</a><br />\n<br />\n其實專業既警員已經完美示範點樣掉,雖然佢係柒咗<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=94jLVeRpc4M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D94jLVeRpc4M&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8bx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=cba66385\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=94jLVeRpc4M</a><br />\n<br />\n玩鐵餅仲要好好<span style=\"color: red;\">保護雙手</span>,好似射箭咁都要護胸啦<br />\n護手都係一件好普通既事<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i2/693459591/TB2U_nlF1ySBuNjy1zdXXXPxFXa_!!693459591.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fimgextra%2Fi2%2F693459591%2FTB2U_nlF1ySBuNjy1zdXXXPxFXa_%21%21693459591.jpg&h=ce43e486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i3/202266691/TB27ZC.vuuSBuNjSsziXXbq8pXa_!!202266691.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fimgextra%2Fi3%2F202266691%2FTB27ZC.vuuSBuNjSsziXXbq8pXa_%21%21202266691.jpg&h=30b4c125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記住做運動前好好保護自己,<span style=\"color: red;\">放假時練習多啲</span>"},{"pid":"9b1556cf2eab9313d0092fa92f061326e04b8681","tid":1525844,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:16:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721/831無獎問答遊戲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試分辨以上事件</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqzkvvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqzkvvH.jpg&h=849fcb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月，機場見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c5bdd79b681ffd06e56679058988ccc59779343c","tid":1525844,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:26:28.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"122673aaaedd18e3902edd477947a8732d6184b6","tid":1525844,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:41:04.000Z","msg":"推 2/10"},{"pid":"fa5b9388e0aaade73e4d2d108a0ee29ab40e3107","tid":1525844,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:44:27.000Z","msg":"推 3/10"},{"pid":"e097d8d4109a44108c3455c010240997a77ff250","tid":1525844,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:44:39.000Z","msg":"推 4/10"},{"pid":"8e95a75ffb2cc128a6f3270ada647d7bfb67fc03","tid":1525844,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:45:28.000Z","msg":"推 5/10"},{"pid":"3a02e6367520a80f5e795e73f9d76d3098ba44d1","tid":1525844,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:46:14.000Z","msg":"推 6/10"},{"pid":"36b8120c